.SH NAME
metric2imperial \- Convert metric units to imperial units
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B metric2imperial
[\fI\,OPTIONS\/\fR] \fI\,COMMAND\/\fR [\fI\,NUMBER\/\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B metric2imperial
is a command-line unit conversion utility that converts metric measurements to imperial units and performs currency conversion from Euro to US Dollar. It provides simple, fast conversions with optional desktop notifications and uses bc (basic calculator) for precise decimal calculations.
.PP
The script simplifies unit conversion by providing temperature conversion (Celsius to Fahrenheit), length conversion (millimeters, centimeters, meters to inches and feet), distance conversion (kilometers to miles), currency conversion (Euro to USD with live exchange rates), desktop notifications for conversion results, configurable exchange rate with API updates, numeric input validation, and bc-based precision calculations with 2 decimal places.
.PP
metric2imperial is particularly useful for quick command-line conversions, shell script integration for automated calculations, international collaboration with unit conversions, travel and navigation (distance, temperature, measurements), scientific and engineering work requiring unit conversion, and financial calculations with currency conversion.
